<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧٠٠٨ - حدثنا يزيد بن هارون عن حبيب عن عمرو بن <span class="c2">(هرم)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> قال: <span class="c2">(سئل)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> جابر بن زيد <span class="c2">(عن)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> جارية كانت لرجل <span class="c2">(فمس)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> قبلها بيده أو<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٣٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(أبصر)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> عورتها ثم وهبها لابن له <span class="c2">(أيصح)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">(له)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span> أن <span class="c2">(يطأها)</span> <span class="c2">(٨)</span> قال: لا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
